{"tid":300562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亞洲「最強驅逐艦」055 曝塗裝照   最快明天下水","createTime":"2017-06-28T04:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T06:20:58.000Z","uid":58099,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"015fd5925bd6e10e64d2ff3e982fba40c6f3655d","tid":300562,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/28/122235_0c1c6c0e27c0af26c1d8fa182c1c685b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F28%2F122235_0c1c6c0e27c0af26c1d8fa182c1c685b.jpg&h=72312f2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國軍事網站曝光照片，疑似是解放軍055型的驅逐艦的大型戰艦，已塗上標準軍艦油漆、以及中國國旗。軍事評論家相信，這意味亞洲最強驅逐艦的055型艦，將於近日下水。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港軍事評論員梁國樑說，據此推測，這艘軍艦應該在1至2天內下水。但他指，儘管055驅逐艦下水，但仍要進行栖裝，估計尚未能在短期內服役。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，055大型驅逐艦是亞洲排水量最大的驅逐艦。網絡資料顯示，它的排水量超過1.2萬噸，擁有超過110座以上的飛彈垂直發射單元，遠遠超過052D型的64個。"},{"pid":"d91217bba9e01d448d8f540abb3a3d6f56440d37","tid":300562,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:25:56.000Z","msg":"亞洲亞洲！"},{"pid":"391f8774ca14a6e1800315edfb929ecf31b83c27","tid":300562,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:28:54.000Z","msg":"中國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0474f6cef80b06a544c96611a9b93d2c6b35312d","tid":300562,"uid":32676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:33:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b0/USS_Zumwalt_%28DDG-1000%29_at_night.jpg/1920px-USS_Zumwalt_%28DDG-1000%29_at_night.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fb%2Fb0%2FUSS_Zumwalt_%2528DDG-1000%2529_at_night.jpg%2F1920px-USS_Zumwalt_%2528DDG-1000%2529_at_night.jpg&h=4deaeee4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"715ac59d8af509c1b9ef4eeb5596c981fb7b5cea","tid":300562,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:44:08.000Z","msg":"123"},{"pid":"5dca000ddbf771127be0c080f5c555518ad9eede","tid":300562,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:45:43.000Z","msg":"亞洲最強? 點強法？<br />\n<br />\n日本算唔算亞洲?<br />\n<br />\n第七艦隊算唔亞洲？"},{"pid":"f76004cba77404baae8c03d331f58e63f0fb946a","tid":300562,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:47:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>亞洲最強? 點強法？<br />\n<br />\n日本算唔算亞洲?<br />\n<br />\n第七艦隊算唔亞洲？</blockquote><br />\n講緊驅逐艦<br />\n<br />\n你做乜鳩"},{"pid":"b16a49508d90da99406bd4a8da89e9ebe0d69d2d","tid":300562,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>亞洲最強? 點強法？<br />\n<br />\n日本算唔算亞洲?<br />\n<br />\n第七艦隊算唔亞洲？</blockquote><br />\n講緊驅逐艦<br />\n<br />\n你做乜鳩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係講緊驅逐艦<br />\n<br />\n你做乜鳩？"},{"pid":"59118de48dbf4a91bd4e4ecf13cf0107def77025","tid":300562,"uid":11092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:51:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/lUWpKYeZU3Y/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FlUWpKYeZU3Y%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=a2772969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人唔笑"},{"pid":"e42e215e376dfe0a6c337bd9bd1b5420ac02e39f","tid":300562,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:52:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/lUWpKYeZU3Y/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FlUWpKYeZU3Y%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=a2772969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人唔笑</blockquote><br />\n習近平都吠"},{"pid":"8bf68f513eb0a1a8aa72644ebdb4bb0b0b2d2103","tid":300562,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:54:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/lUWpKYeZU3Y/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FlUWpKYeZU3Y%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=a2772969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人唔笑</blockquote><br />\n習近平都吠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本脫亞入歐, <br />\n可能五毛當佢係歐洲"},{"pid":"97e17b1dd066819bac2e8a9e265f0ff583ac6c6e","tid":300562,"uid":9141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:56:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a24d9332af7e3ba9a57f99385915963153d0696","tid":300562,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:59:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/lUWpKYeZU3Y/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FlUWpKYeZU3Y%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=a2772969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人唔笑</blockquote><br />\n排水量幾多<br />\n<br />\n發射單元幾多"},{"pid":"5c630a24fcd3a4ecd9368779ad22bcb75607e367","tid":300562,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T05:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/lUWpKYeZU3Y/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FlUWpKYeZU3Y%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=a2772969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人唔笑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n理論上, 日本堆 DDH 都係驅逐艦<br />\n<br />\n再講, 俄佬起緊既17,500噸「領袖23560」（23560 Lider）仲癲<br />\n&gt; 200粒彈<br />\n<br />\n會係太平洋部署6隻<br />\n<br />\n唔知五毛當唔當俄佬係亞洲?"},{"pid":"db7496a82a0e5f2dfc48c02580b9a6cc03cd331e","tid":300562,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T05:05:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/lUWpKYeZU3Y/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FlUWpKYeZU3Y%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=a2772969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人唔笑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n理論上, 日本堆 DDH 都係驅逐艦<br />\n<br />\n再講, 俄佬起緊既17,500噸「領袖23560」（23560 Lider）仲癲<br />\n&gt; 200粒彈<br />\n<br />\n會係太平洋部署6隻<br />\n<br />\n唔知五毛當唔當俄佬係亞洲?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n據俄羅斯媒體報道，已經「醞釀」了很久的俄羅斯海軍造艦計劃終於有了結果，俄海軍新一代「領袖」級驅逐艦的外觀已經確定，該艦排水量將達到10000噸，主要動力裝置為燃氣渦輪型，徹底放棄了核動力，這是一個最大的改變，預計將於2018年開建，共計劃建12艘該級別驅逐艦。<br />\n<br />\n「領袖」級驅逐艦模型<br />\n軍事專家巡航者介紹，俄羅斯北方設計局早就始立項設計23560型「領袖級」核動力驅逐艦的技術方案，原來的方案是排水量將為1.75萬噸，接近俄海軍最大的1144型核動力導彈巡洋艦「彼得大帝」號。現在排水量降低不少，動力也從核動力改為常規動力。「領袖」級驅逐艦是俄羅斯海軍目前設計的的作戰能力最強的一款驅逐艦，在隱身、打擊火力等很多方面有重大超越。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/military/n593jk8.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fmilitary%2Fn593jk8.html&d=u1%2FEs3OS3SrFj2rHSft%2FFTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=6400aa9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/military/n593jk8.html</a>"},{"pid":"bfa4e1d234d02a0d71de43ba632fccd6b683402e","tid":300562,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T05:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de6d991ecb1da198c78d71371af85899abdf4713","tid":300562,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T05:25:14.000Z","msg":"最強潛水艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284906f48bcb572848b6f6213ef88341cd5a650a","tid":300562,"uid":34098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T05:25:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/lUWpKYeZU3Y/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FlUWpKYeZU3Y%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=a2772969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人唔笑</blockquote><br />\n排水量幾多<br />\n<br />\n發射單元幾多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隻戰艦勁唔勁，唔係單睇排水，發射單元<br />\n美國伯克(包括一樣動力系統既日本ddg)最高記錄航速有34節，聽聞大陸055最高得30節，因為發動機水平差過人。<br />\n導彈質素又遠遠差過美國，雷達又係落後美國(相對較少)。諗唔明點解會係亞洲最勁。<br />\n<br />\n如果計噸位=勁，太和號又係唔係應該排名在055之上？"},{"pid":"b257e19d7364199918a1635acfbca8d7b0aae1c1","tid":300562,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T05:26:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/lUWpKYeZU3Y/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FlUWpKYeZU3Y%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=a2772969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人唔笑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n理論上, 日本堆 DDH 都係驅逐艦<br />\n<br />\n再講, 俄佬起緊既17,500噸「領袖23560」（23560 Lider）仲癲<br />\n&gt; 200粒彈<br />\n<br />\n會係太平洋部署6隻<br />\n<br />\n唔知五毛當唔當俄佬係亞洲?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n據俄羅斯媒體報道，已經「醞釀」了很久的俄羅斯海軍造艦計劃終於有了結果，俄海軍新一代「領袖」級驅逐艦的外觀已經確定，該艦排水量將達到10000噸，主要動力裝置為燃氣渦輪型，徹底放棄了核動力，這是一個最大的改變，預計將於2018年開建，共計劃建12艘該級別驅逐艦。<br />\n<br />\n「領袖」級驅逐艦模型<br />\n軍事專家巡航者介紹，俄羅斯北方設計局早就始立項設計23560型「領袖級」核動力驅逐艦的技術方案，原來的方案是排水量將為1.75萬噸，接近俄海軍最大的1144型核動力導彈巡洋艦「彼得大帝」號。現在排水量降低不少，動力也從核動力改為常規動力。「領袖」級驅逐艦是俄羅斯海軍目前設計的的作戰能力最強的一款驅逐艦，在隱身、打擊火力等很多方面有重大超越。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/military/n593jk8.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fmilitary%2Fn593jk8.html&d=u1%2FEs3OS3SrFj2rHSft%2FFTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=6400aa9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/military/n593jk8.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你POST個CONTENT FARM做乜鳩？"},{"pid":"d93d92712a10fd5b977345a562d28f2850841f56","tid":300562,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T05:27:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/lUWpKYeZU3Y/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FlUWpKYeZU3Y%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=a2772969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人唔笑</blockquote><br />\n排水量幾多<br />\n<br />\n發射單元幾多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隻戰艦勁唔勁，唔係單睇排水，發射單元<br />\n美國伯克(包括一樣動力系統既日本ddg)最高記錄航速有34節，聽聞大陸055最高得30節，因為發動機水平差過人。<br />\n導彈質素又遠遠差過美國，雷達又係落後美國(相對較少)。諗唔明點解會係亞洲最勁。<br />\n<br />\n如果計噸位=勁，太和號又係唔係應該排名在055之上？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n北洋艦隊 總噸位都大過 日本聯合艦隊<br />\n北洋艦隊 主炮火力亦都勁過 日本聯合艦隊<br />\n結果呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4583ae210a68033c7562710b4d865460b3c3376","tid":300562,"uid":34098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T05:34:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/lUWpKYeZU3Y/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FlUWpKYeZU3Y%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=a2772969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人唔笑</blockquote><br />\n排水量幾多<br />\n<br />\n發射單元幾多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隻戰艦勁唔勁，唔係單睇排水，發射單元<br />\n美國伯克(包括一樣動力系統既日本ddg)最高記錄航速有34節，聽聞大陸055最高得30節，因為發動機水平差過人。<br />\n導彈質素又遠遠差過美國，雷達又係落後美國(相對較少)。諗唔明點解會係亞洲最勁。<br />\n<br />\n如果計噸位=勁，太和號又係唔係應該排名在055之上？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n北洋艦隊 總噸位都大過 日本聯合艦隊<br />\n北洋艦隊 主炮火力亦都勁過 日本聯合艦隊<br />\n結果呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算啦，由得五毛打飛機喇。"},{"pid":"9ea5883088218c08edbed78b907bff50cc11e78e","tid":300562,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T05:44:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b0/USS_Zumwalt_%28DDG-1000%29_at_night.jpg/1920px-USS_Zumwalt_%28DDG-1000%29_at_night.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fb%2Fb0%2FUSS_Zumwalt_%2528DDG-1000%2529_at_night.jpg%2F1920px-USS_Zumwalt_%2528DDG-1000%2529_at_night.jpg&h=4deaeee4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個字~ 型仔~"},{"pid":"60295c53a55da436b9519f67b121644151369f56","tid":300562,"uid":67444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:11:36.000Z","msg":"聽日就可以落水打飛機了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377eed461de649cc180ef1146d8c2840e5083895","tid":300562,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b0/USS_Zumwalt_%28DDG-1000%29_at_night.jpg/1920px-USS_Zumwalt_%28DDG-1000%29_at_night.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fb%2Fb0%2FUSS_Zumwalt_%2528DDG-1000%2529_at_night.jpg%2F1920px-USS_Zumwalt_%2528DDG-1000%2529_at_night.jpg&h=4deaeee4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個字~ 型仔~</blockquote><br />\n隱形Ddg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}